name: Easol
headline: Shopify for experiences
description:
Easol is the all-in-one platform for managing your entire experience business, on your terms. Sell directly on your own website with smart booking, payment, and marketing tools that all work together, brilliantly.

We believe that with the right tools, anyone can turn their passion into an empire. So we made them – and brought them together to work in sync, all in one place.

We call it Experience Commerce. It's e-commerce specially designed for selling experiences and especially designed for experience creators.

# your way
Easol is the all-in-one platform for managing your entire experience business, on your terms. Build your website, sell and manage bookings, control your fees and payment options, and own your brand and data.
[Book a Demo](http://www.easol.com/</book-a-demo>)
![a girl crowdsurfing at a festival](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2Fhome-3.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
The problem
## The old ways of selling experiences don't work
Platforms that aren't built for you
You've had to force fit your business into tools not made for selling experiences, or even build solutions yourself that are difficult to maintain and don't scale.
TOO MANY TOOLS, NOT WORKING TOGETHER
From ticketing and payments processing, to managing bookings and analytics, you've had to stitch together multiple platforms to bring your experience to life.
SERVICES THAT CONTROL YOUR BRAND and DATA
You've used tools that force you to adapt to their branding instead of building your own storefront, giving up control of your brand and your customer data.
Websites
## Own your brand and storefront
Your website is your brand's masterpiece, and Easol combines best-in-class web design with modular store building. Pick a theme, customise your booking journey, and for the first time ever, own your entire customer experience.
Replaces web design tools like Squarespace, WordPress, Webflow and Wix
Replaces hosting platforms like Eventbrite and DesignMyNight
[Learn moreArrow pointing to the right](http://www.easol.com/<https:/easol.com/products#web-builder>)
![A browser window displaying a website and metrics](http://www.easol.com/images/homepage/6.jpg)
Selling & Managing Bookings
## Sell any experience, any day, anywhere
Selling experiences goes beyond just ticketing, and with Easol, you can include accommodations, transportation, add-ons, and custom packages that group them all together. And a unified platform means one backend for managing your bookings.
Replaces ticketing platforms like Ticketmaster, Eventix, SeeTickets and Kaboodle
Replaces booking platforms like BookNow, Peek and SevenRooms
[Learn moreArrow pointing to the right](http://www.easol.com/<https:/easol.com/products#selling-tools>)
![A Moroccan Riad](http://www.easol.com/images/homepage/6.jpg)
Payments
## Get Paid in ways your Customers will love
Easy for them, automatic for you. Watch your booking conversions soar by offering customers flexible options – pay with deposits or payment plans, individually or in groups, in their currency or yours, and more.
Replaces payment tools like Stripe, Partially and Paypal
Integrates with payment methods like Apple Pay, Google Pay and Klarna
[Learn moreArrow pointing to the right](http://www.easol.com/<https:/easol.com/products#payments>)
![Women riding camels in the desert](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2F5.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Marketing
## Own your data to grow faster, smarter
Grow your business like a global enterprise when you own your customer data. Create personalised recommendations and upsells, start ambassador programs, and customise pricing and promotions to drive business results.
Integrates with marketing analytics tools through Google Tag Manager
[Learn moreArrow pointing to the right](http://www.easol.com/<https:/easol.com/products#marketing>)
![A festival stage in the daylight](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2F7.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Build for any type of experience

From yoga retreats in Costa Rica and music festivals in the Sahara, to fishing trips in Wyoming and putt putt in Dubai, Easol can help turn your passion into a thriving business, and your business into an empire.

  * #### Adventure

  * #### Food & Drink

TESTIMONIALS
# Creator Love
![A festival crowd on a hilltop](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2Ftestimonials%2F7.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Charlie - Meadows in the Mountains
Ticket sales increased 80% after switching to Easol!
We have sold more tickets, accommodation options and extra experiences, and as a result achieved significantly more revenue with Easol than any other platform in the 10 year history of our festival.
[Visit Website](http://www.easol.com/<https:/www.meadowsinthemountains.com/>)
![A tribal woman staring at the camera](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2Ftestimonials%2F8.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Sean - Wanderlust
We partnered with Easol to take Wanderlust to the next level.
Easol is the holy trinity – enabling us to handle ticketing, lodging and scheduling too, The team at Easol really understand the complexity of our business as they used to run complex events themselves.
[Visit Website](http://www.easol.com/<https:/wanderlust.com/>)
![A fit man jumping forwards](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2Ftestimonials%2F2.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Mantas - Surf Yoga Beer
Using Easol was the best decision we made for our business!
The expertise and enthusiasm about our field of business is quite something - as a partner Easol is dedicated to helping us with the success of our business. Not to mention lightning support responses even at 1am!
[Visit Website](http://www.easol.com/<https:/www.surfyogabeer.com/>)
![two girls playing netball](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2Ftestimonials%2Fb7.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Craig - Bournemouth 7's Festival
Easol's partnership helped make our 15th year a huge success!
We want to thank you to the whole Easol team for their end to end support and the team's contribution in to making Bournemouth 7s Festival 15th year the huge success it was!
[Visit Website](http://www.easol.com/<https:/www.bournemouth7s.com/>)
![a festival crowd at sunset](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2Ftestimonials%2Fenvision.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Sean - Envision
We multiplied our revenue by 6x using Easol this year
One of the key features we used was payment plans which 90% of our customers book with and love. The office hours are also super valuable, I love being able to spitball ideas with the team and the support is fantastic! They really deliver on everything they say they will do.
[Visit Website](http://www.easol.com/<https:/www.envisionfestival.com/>)
![a woman dj-ing](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2Ftestimonials%2Fhide.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Kurt - Hide & Seek
Our marketing spend became 70% more efficient
Easol allowed us to offer flexible payment options to our customers. We ran ads around it, we launched email marketing, we promoted it on the website. It had such a high return, so we doubled down, resulting in our biggest number of sales to date!
[Visit Website](http://www.easol.com/<https:/www.hideandseekfestival.co.uk/>)
![a marathon runner in a race](http://www.easol.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhomepage%2Ftestimonials%2Fboulderthon.jpg&w=3840&q=75)
Phil - Boulderthon
We've doubled our number of participants!
We're so thrilled to have doubled our participant cap to 8,000, up from 4,000 last year. This explosive growth made partnering with Easol a logical next step as we continue to establish ourselves as a premier U.S. marathon.
[Visit Website](http://www.easol.com/<https:/www.boulderthon.org/>)

We believe that with the right tools, anyone can turn their passion into an empire. So we made them.

### Easol: Empowering Experience Creators

**Company Overview:**
Easol is an innovative platform launched in 2017, designed to transform how experience creators manage their businesses. Think of it as “Shopify for experiences.” It enables users to sell directly through their own websites while integrating booking, payment, and marketing tools seamlessly.

**Mission:**
Easol's mission is simple yet profound: to help anyone turn their passion into a legitimate business. They believe that with the right tools, anyone can build an empire from their experiences—be it a yoga retreat in Costa Rica, a music festival in the Sahara, or culinary tours in Italy.

**What They Do:**
Easol is at the forefront of a new concept called **Experience Commerce.** This is e-commerce tailored specifically for selling experiences. The platform offers a range of tools that allow experience creators to:
- Build their own customizable websites 
- Manage bookings and reservations 
- Sell tickets, accommodations, and more 
- Control payment options and optimize marketing strategies 
- Analyze data for continuous growth

**Key Features:**
1. **Web Builder**: Craft your brand’s unique online presence.
2. **Booking Manager**: Streamline the booking process for your customers.
3. **Selling Tools**: Offer diverse products, including tickets and accommodations, all in one place.
4. **Marketing Insights**: Gain insights into customer behavior for targeted marketing.
5. **Flexible Payments**: Offer customers a variety of payment methods (e.g., deposits, payment plans).

**Target Industries:**
Easol caters to a wide array of experience businesses, including:
- Festivals (music, art, food)
- Sports events (marathons, triathlons)
- Wellness retreats
- Adventure tours (hiking, gaming, travel)

**Achievements & Recognition:**
Founded in London and part of the Y Combinator Batch S18, Easol has grown to a team of 70 passionate employees. Notable figures include Michael Seibel, serving as their Group Partner. Their impressive growth reflects their commitment to supporting experience creators globally.

**Community and Support:**
Easol isn’t just a platform; it’s a community. With resources like the MUSE blog, real-life case studies, customer support services, and access to funding through Easol Capital, the company empowers its users with the tools and knowledge needed for success.

**User Testimonials:**
Easol has already made a significant impact on its users. For instance, a music festival reported an 80% increase in ticket sales after switching to Easol. The platform’s flexibility and dedicated support have been key to transforming various businesses from simple venues to thriving experiences.

To learn more about what Easol can do, check out their website at [easol.com](http://www.easol.com) and see how they might help you turn your passion into profit.
